idare.Properties

Class IDAREProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • idare.Properties.IDAREProperties

  • public class IDAREProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing all static Fields for the IDARE Columns. Please use only these fields when altering IDARE columns.
    Author:
    Thomas PFau

      • IDARE_NODE_UID

        public static final java.lang.String IDARE_NODE_UID
        The ID for this node if it is the target of a link. At network creation this will be set to the SUID of the corresponding node. It should never ever be overwritten Link Nodes should (in general) not have this property set.
